snippet.textDisplay: This is my favourite buffet of all time :3 I really like strawberry shortcake and mekajiki sashimi and kept calling the restaurant to try my luck and see when both items would be served at the buffet. After the 3rd call, they finally told me that the buffet on XX date would have those items and when I went for the buffet, the two items were served directly to my table at no additional cost :O Both items were actually not available on the main buffet tables but they gave me an entire strawberry shortcake and unlimited mekajiki on top of the full buffet spread. The service was impeccable and the desserts kept changing. I think they basically cut all their gourmet cakes that aren't sold for the day for the buffet so I could try them all :P
